---
---

<section class="cta">
  <div class="wrap cta__inner reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Get in touch</p>
    <h2 class="cta__title">
      I'm always up for a good<br class="cta__br" />
      conversation about <span class="serif-italic">applied AI.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="cta__lede">
      Working on something interesting in AI products?
      Whether it's a question, a collaboration, or just a chat—I'd love to hear about it.
    </p>
    <div class="cta__actions">
      <a href="mailto:ansaldo.gabri@gmail.com" class="btn">
        ansaldo.gabri@gmail.com
        <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabrieleansaldo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost">
        LinkedIn
        <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 10rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .cta__inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.8rem;
  }

  .cta__title {
    font-family: 'Inter Tight', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin: 0.4rem 0 0 0;
  }

  .cta__lede {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.6vw, 1.35rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--mute);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta__br {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
